---------------------------------------------------------------------
 Index Scan Backward using _id_ on documentdb_data.documents_18401_1840002 collection
   Output: document, bson_orderby(document, '{ "_id" : { "$numberInt" : "-1" } }'::bson)
   Index Cond: (collection.shard_key_value = '18401'::bigint)
(3 rows)

EXPLAIN (COSTS OFF, VERBOSE ON) SELECT document FROM bson_aggregation_find('pkdb', '{ "find": "pk_native", "filter": { "_id": { "$gt": 0 } }, "sort": { "_id": 1 } }');
                                                                                                     QUERY PLAN                                                                                                      
---------------------------------------------------------------------
